    <item>
      <title>卢比奥说，我们不会退出北约推动国防支出</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/europe-must-diversify-defense-from-us-eu-s-top-diplomat-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[国务卿马可·鲁比奥（Marco Rubio）坚持认为，唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）的政府无意离开北约，即使美国特使要求军事联盟成员棘手支出。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/europe-must-diversify-defense-from-us-eu-s-top-diplomat-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Apr 2025 08:08:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>匈牙利退出ICC，因为内塔尼亚胡在访问期间违反了逮捕令</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/hungary-set-to-start-process-of-exiting-icc-minister-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[匈牙利宣布退出国际刑事法院，总理维克多·奥尔班（Viktor Orban）在布达佩斯（Budapest）接待了本杰明·内塔尼亚胡（Benjamin Netanyahu），无视以色列领导人的逮捕令。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/hungary-set-to-start-process-of-exiting-icc-minister-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Apr 2025 08:02:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>对于世界上最贫穷的国家来说，特朗普关税是一场“灾难”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/trump-tariffs-are-disaster-for-the-world-s-poorest-countries</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）总统的新互惠关税将遭受世界上最贫穷的国家的最难打击，这使他们的劳动密集型出口行业处于危险之中，并降低了美国比竞争对手中国最大的经济优势之一。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/trump-tariffs-are-disaster-for-the-world-s-poorest-countries</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Apr 2025 07:35:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
